title: and James Kennedy
description:
Have you been jonesing for a little James Kennedy? Well, he's back and talking about his so-called crazy life! He's got stories about his jet-setting DJ tour, dealing with screaming fans, fist-fights and ballyhoo, and keeping sane on long flights! Plus, Randall's in Puerto Rico shooting his first movie, and gives an update from location, and he and LaLa answer some more voicemail!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
